msgstr "Ahh, I love him..."

#: 0037BC78
msgid ""
"番人：今はそこを通すわけにはいかない。"
msgstr ""

#: 0037BCA2
msgid ""
"あせらず時を待ちなさい。"
msgstr ""

#: 0037BCF1
msgid ""
"番人：今はそこを通すわけにはいかない。"
msgstr ""

#: 0037BD1B
msgid ""
"あせらず時を待ちなさい。"
msgstr ""

#: 0037BD89
msgid ""
"番人：お前さん達はもうそこには用はないはずじゃ。"
msgstr ""

#: 0037BDEF
msgid ""
"カイ：番人のおじいさんにほうこくしてこよう。"
msgstr "Kai: Let's report to the guard what happened."

#: 0037BE1F
msgid ""
"帰るのはそれからでも遅くないはずだ。"
msgstr ""

#: 0037BE5A
msgid ""
"カイ：番人のおじいさんにあいさつしてこよう。"
msgstr "Kai: Let's go say hi to the guard."

#: 0037BE8A
msgid ""
"帰るのはそれからでも遅くないはずだ。"
msgstr "It shouldn't take us too long."

#: 0037BEF1
msgid ""
"カイ：今、逃げ出しては来た意味が無いな。"
msgstr "Kai: Why even come here if we're just gonna leave?"

#: 0037BF53
msgid ""
"番人：今はそこを通すわけにはいかない。"
msgstr ""

#: 0037BF7D
msgid ""
"あせらず時を待ちなさい。"
msgstr ""

#: 0037BFD2
msgid ""
"番人：今はそこを通すわけにはいかない。"
msgstr "Guard: You cannot pass right now."

#: 0037BFFC
msgid ""
"あせらず時を待ちなさい。"
msgstr "Please be patient and relax."

#: 0037C05D
msgid ""
"番人：お前さん達はもうそこには用はないはずじゃ。"
msgstr "Guard: There shouldn't be any reason for you to go through anymore."

#: 0037C1AD
msgid ""
"バーク：どうしたんだい、ミシリアちゃん。こんな夜更けに。"
msgstr "Burke: What's wrong, Michelia? It's really late."

#: 0037C203
msgid ""
"ミシリア：バークさん・・・"
msgstr "Michelia: Burke..."

#: 0037C251
msgid ""
"ミシリア：なんでもないんです。ただちょっと夜風に当たりたくて。"
msgstr "Michelia: I-it's nothing. I just wanted to feel the night breeze."

#: 0037C2AC
msgid ""
"バーク：カイのことか？"
msgstr "Burke: Thinking 'bout Kai?"

#: 0037C2DF
msgid ""
"ミシリア：・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・"
msgstr "Michelia: ..."

#: 0037C320
msgid ""
"ミシリア：なんだかあの人を遠くに感じるの・・・"
msgstr "Michelia: ...he feels really far away all of a sudden..."

#: 0037C360
msgid ""
"バーク：カイが王子様だと知ってからか？"
msgstr "Burke: Since he became a prince and all?"

#: 0037C3A3
msgid ""
"ミシリア：うん・・・"
msgstr "Michelia: Well..."

#: 0037C3D4
msgid ""
"バーク：なーに気にする事はねぇ。"
msgstr "Burke: Come on, don't worry about that."

#: 0037C3F8
msgid ""
"あいつは何もかわっちゃいねぇよ。"
msgstr "You know that kid hasn't changed."

#: 0037C41C
msgid ""
"かわったのは、むしろミシリアちゃんの方だぜ？"
msgstr "Don't you think you're the one who changed?"

#: 0037C465
msgid ""
"ミシリア：私？"
msgstr "Michelia: Me?"

#: 0037C485
msgid ""
"バーク：そうさ、カイが王子様だからって自分から遠ざかって、"
msgstr "Burke: Yup, YOU'RE the one who bailed on him after finding out."

#: 0037C4C3
msgid ""
"王子様が私なんかにふり向いてくれないだろうって、勝手に思いこんでる。"
msgstr "\"A prince wouldn't want to be near something like me!\""

#: 0037C50B
msgid ""
"違うかい？"
msgstr "Thinking like that, am I right?"

#: 0037C532
msgid ""
"ミシリア：・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・"
msgstr ""

#: 0037C579
msgid ""
"バーク：そんなことじゃ、ファラにカイを取られちまうぜ。"
msgstr "Burke: Keep thinking like that and Fara will take him."

#: 0037C5B3
msgid ""
"あいつは自分の気持ちに正直だからな。"
msgstr "She's at least honest with her feelings."

#: 0037C5DE
msgid ""
"じっさい、カイが王子様だってこと、これっぽっちも気にしちゃいねぇ。"
msgstr "Really just forget about the whole prince thing."

#: 0037C624
msgid ""
"カイが好きだってことだけでついてきてる。"
msgstr "All that matters is that you like him."

#: 0037C65B
msgid ""
"ミシリアちゃんだってカイが好きだからついて来たんだろう？"
msgstr "That's the reason you came on this journey, right?"

#: 0037C6A5
msgid ""
"ミシリア：・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・"
msgstr ""

#: 0037C6EC
msgid ""
"バーク：・・・・あーよけいなこといっちまったみたいだな。"
msgstr "Burke: ...ah, might have said a bit too much there."

#: 0037C72B
msgid ""
"まぁ、気にせずにカイにアタックしてみちゃどうだ？"
msgstr "Anyway, just throw caution to the wind and push your way to Kai's side."

#: 0037C75F
msgid ""
"あいつはあーいう性格だからなかなか自分でいいだせねぇと思うしよ。"
msgstr ""
"He's a nervous kid himself, so you know HE'S not gonna admit his feelings "
"either."

#: 0037C7A6
msgid ""
"それに・・・"
msgstr "Also..."

#: 0037C7B6
msgid ""
"自信もちなよ。ミシリアちゃんはそこらのおひめ様よりきれいだからよ"
msgstr "Have some confidence! You're prettier than any princess out there!"

#: 0037C808
msgid ""
"ミシリア：・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・"
msgstr "Michelia: ..."

#: 0037C8A2
msgid ""
"ミシリア：あ、あの・・・"
msgstr "Michelia: U-umm...!"

#: 0037C905
msgid ""
"ミシリア：ありがとう。バークさん。"
msgstr "Michelia: Thanks, Burke."

#: 0037CA5B
msgid ""
"カイ：ミシリア。どうしたの、こんな遅くに"
msgstr "Kai: Michelia, what're you doing up so late?"

#: 0037CAB2
msgid ""
"ミシリア：カイ！！"
msgstr "Michelia: Kai!"

#: 0037CACB
msgid ""
"カイこそどうして・・・"
msgstr "I could ask you the same thing, Kai..."

#: 0037CAFE
msgid ""
"カイ：んー、バークが話があるから外で待ってろって・・・"
msgstr "Kai: Well, Burke told me he had something to talk about outside..."

#: 0037CB46
msgid ""
"ミシリア：そ、そう。"
msgstr "Michelia: I-I see."

#: 0037CB88
msgid ""
"カイ：・・・・・・・・・・"
msgstr "Kai: ..."

#: 0037CBB4
msgid ""
"ミシリア：・・・・・・・・・"
msgstr "Michelia: ..."

#: 0037CC01
msgid ""
"カイ＆ミシリア：あ、あの・・・・"
msgstr ""

#: 0037CC3E
msgid ""
"カイ：な、何、ミシリア・・・"
msgstr "Kai: W-what is it, Michelia...?"

#: 0037CC77
msgid ""
"ミシリア：カイのほうこそ・・・何・・・"
msgstr "Michelia: No, no. You first..."

#: 0037CD06
msgid ""
"カイ＆ミシリア：あ、あの・・・・"
msgstr "Kai & Michelia: U-umm..."

#: 0037CD43
msgid ""
"カイ：ミシリアから・・・"
msgstr "Kai: It's okay, go ahead..."

#: 0037CD78
msgid ""
"ミシリア：カイのほうから・・・"
msgstr "Michelia: I insist, go ahead..."

#: 0037CDEE
msgid ""
"カイ：あのさ・・・"
msgstr "Kai: Umm..."

#: 0037CE28
msgid ""
"カイ：メルーの町でさ、ミシリアが僕について行きたいって"
msgstr "Kai: In Mell, you said you wanted to come with me."

#: 0037CE62
msgid ""
"言ってくれた時、あの、その・・・とてもうれしかった。"
msgstr "That, umm... well... made me really happy."

#: 0037CEA8
msgid ""
"どうしてもこれがいいたかったんだけど、最近、なかなか"
msgstr "I thought everything would be great after that, but lately,"

#: 0037CEE0
msgid ""
"話すじかんがなくてさ・・・"
msgstr "we haven't had any time to talk..."

#: 0037CF30
msgid ""
"カイ：そ、それじゃ・・・"
msgstr "Kai: S-so..."

#: 0037CF86
msgid ""
"ミシリア：あ・・・"
msgstr "Michelia: Ah..."

#: 0037CFAA
msgid ""
"ミシリア：待って！！"
msgstr "Michelia: Wait!"

#: 0037D015
msgid ""
"カイ：ミ、ミシリア・・・"
msgstr "Kai: M-Michelia..."

#: 0037D042
msgid ""
"ミシリア：・・・・・・・・"
msgstr "Michelia: ..."

#: 0037D071
msgid ""
"カイ：・・・・・・・"
msgstr ""

#: 0037D09A
msgid ""
"ミシリア：私、カイにずっとついていきたい！！"
msgstr "Michelia: I always want to be with you!"

#: 0037D0CA
msgid ""
"カイが王子様だってかまわない。ずっと・・・ずっと・・"
msgstr "I don't care that you're a prince. I always... always..."

#: 0037D113
msgid ""
"ミシリア：私、私・・・"
msgstr "Michelia: I..."

#: 0037D176
msgid ""
"カイ：ミシリア・・・"
msgstr "Kai: Michelia..."

#: 0037D1C3
msgid ""
"ミシリア：カイ・・・"
msgstr "Michelia: Kai..."

#: 0037D267
